== Overview ==
The Sentinel class tracker chassis is a heavy defensive unit. Its hull was inspired by the body of a snail, containing a single tracked 'foot' and a strong shell. The Sentinel has the potent ability to project its own shield power off its specially designed shell covering other squad members. The projected shield can become very powerful due to the Sentinel's ability to carry up to three heavy shield generators. The Sentinel however is offensively weak. Its forward facing weapon slots, slow turn rate and low profile equates to a poorer than average accuracy and damage rating.

Sells for 38000 credits.

